snippet.title: Festive Mash-up Pack
snippet.description:
Celebrate the Festive period with this wintery mash-up pack containing a Festive style Texture Pack, Skin Pack, new music and a Festive world!
The mash-up pack is available now on Xbox One and Xbox 360.
